<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="B" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Babylon" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Babylon,</orth> the famous ancient town: <cit><quote>when as I sat in Pabylon,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.1.24" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. III, 1, 24</bibl></cit> (Evans' song). <cit><quote>there dwelt a man in B.,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tn 2.3.84" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. II, 3, 84</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the whore of B.</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 2.3.41" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 II, 3, 41</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>